# 12. Conclusion

This project demonstrates how **statistical analysis can transform raw business data into actionable insights**. By applying hypothesis testing, correlation analysis, and regression modeling, the study reveals that marketing spend has a significant influence on sales performance.

These findings enable businesses to make **data-driven decisions to improve marketing strategies and increase revenue**.

